rcely contested market swisscanto offers its clients a range of products that suit their requirements and are distinguished by an outstanding priceperformance ratio the cantonal banks for their part are present in the whole of switzerland with their blanketcoverage network of branches and are well known for their customer proximity and highly efficient sales and advisory organisation the competitive advantages result from efficiently linking the core competencies of the swisscanto product specialist with those of the qualified customer adviser thanks to the continuity and constancy of its success swisscanto is a highly competitive and reliable partner today the company acquired its strong market position as an asset manager through its aboveaverage track record the success is sustainable in the past few years swisscanto has been repeatedly honoured nationally and internationally as the best fund company the superior performance emphasises the professionalism and competence of the swisscanto groups employees the performanceoriented corporate culture enables highly qualified members of staff to give a top performance in a challenging demanding and motivating environment swisscanto for private clients investment funds  ideal components for investment strategies over the past few years swisscanto has consolidated its strong position as an important player in the swiss fund market as the centre of competence for the cantonal banks fund business swisscanto concentrates on the development and marketing of investment funds in accordance with swiss and luxembourg law in switzerland marketing is carried out primarily through the cantonal banks but also through insurance companies further banks and asset managers as well as through purposefully selected marketing partners in the adjoining countries swisscanto places a range of clearly structured investment funds at the customer advisers disposal for individual investment strategies as components in modern asset management they meet nearly all investor requirements swisscantos investment funds that are managed professionally and for a reasonable fee include money market funds bond funds equity funds portfolio funds real estate funds fund of hedge funds with regard to performance swisscanto figures among the leading providers throughout europe the quality of the funds is scrutinised regularly by independent analysis and rating companies swisscanto investment funds are awarded national and international prizes every year on account of their firstclass peergroup performance lipper and standard and poors have honoured swisscanto in the past few years with numerous fund awards for individual funds fund categories and for the aboveaverage performance of the entire range of funds swisscanto fund desk fund trading a la carte swisscanto makes a trading platform available to the cantonal banks and other fund marketers for handling both swisscanto funds as well as thirdparty funds there are contractual relations with practically all major swiss and international fund providers which makes it possible to offer a wide range of investment funds on very attractive terms fund desk clients are provided with an efficient service for placing transacting and invoicing orders as well as with portfolio management and reporting services the client profits from the cost advantages of a fully automated process for his fund business pension products  additional benefits for private clients swisscanto offers a welldefined range of standardised pension products which it develops and manages primarily for marketing through the cantonal banks the products are specially designed for marketing through banks so that they will bring a clearly apparent additional benefit for private clients in combination with other bank products in the case of a fundlinked insurance within the framework of free pension products pillar b the client profits not only from taxfree investment income but also from all the advantages of a life insurance or the fund saving plan with its extremely flexible payingin arrangements and the option to invest in fund units it acquires the characteristics of a retirement pension product through its organisation as a withdrawal scheme swisscantos pension products are designed for the long term so that expectations aroused at the time of concluding the agreement can indeed be fulfilled after five ten or even more years safeguarding ones personal future is dependent on competent advice an individual pension solution can only be developed with the support of an acknowledged expert in this connection the pension advice offered by the cantonal banks has proved itself through a dynamic advisory process the relevant questions concerning pensions are answered within the framework of an integral overall concept swisscanto provides competitive products for this process maximise yields with securities saving and the swisscanto investment foundation assets in the cantonal banks taxprivileged savings  pension accounts are intended to earn as attractive a yield as possible within the statutory limits within the framework of securities saving these pension monies can be invested in investment groups of the swisscanto investment foundation these investment groups always comply with the statutory investment regulations stipulated by bvv those engaging in securities saving can thus participate in developments both in the economy and on the stock market swisscanto for companies and institutions occupational pensions swisscanto offers companies mainly standard schemes to cover their occupational pension requirements schemes that are easily understandable and can be administered at a reasonable cost at the same time these schemes are sufficiently flexible to allow for clients individual requirements to be satisfied swisscanto collective foundation since its establishment in  the swisscanto collective foundation has developed into one of the most important bank foundations in the staff pension sector in switzerland flexible solutions to suit requirements in the compulsory sector of occupational pension planning as well as easily understandable standard schemes that can be administered at a reasonable cost enjoy top priority under certain conditions the swisscanto collective foundation also offers help with the preparation of individual pension schemes furthermore the affiliated pension institutions have the possibility of influencing how their saving funds are invested provided certain requirements are met swisscanto supra collective foundation the subsidiary foundation swisscanto supra as a specialist in the supracompulsory sector principally covers requirements going beyond the compulsory bvg pension cover it offers solutions in line with the needs of senior management so as to avoid any pension gaps and achieves improvements in benefits for certain categories of persons swisscanto vested benefits foundation the swisscanto vested benefits foundation offers services for cantonal banks which can not or do not want to establish a foundation of their own to run vested benefits accounts if an employee gives up gainful employment temporarily eg on account of further training a stay abroad or also because of unemployment his pension credit balance can be invested in a vested benefits account of the swisscanto vested benefits foundation staff pension solutions for companies as an integrated whole the swisscanto collective foundations most important partners apart from the cantonal banks as marketing partners are the swisscanto investment foundation which is responsible for investment management and helvetia patria as risk insurer simple transparent products optimal advice as well as a professional investment management are the main advantages of a swisscanto staff pension solution pension fund consulting and administration swisscanto is the competent partner for your occupational pensions no matter whether your pension institution is autonomous semiautono