lculations and prepare reports in accordance with international and national accounting standards such as ias  frs fer etc swisscanto for institutional investors consistently implemented investment philosophy swisscanto is an acknowledged specialist in institutional asset management the portfolio management benefits from the investment specialists firstclass qualifications and many years of professional experience in three respects in the case of the swisscanto investment funds in the case of the collective assets of the swisscanto investment foundation and in the case of the asset management mandates for institutional investors swisscantos portfolio management is based on the latest findings of modern portfolio theory here particular importance is attached to controlling and steering investment risks for years swisscanto has been positioning itself successfully by means of the risk premium approach the starting point for strategic investment decisions are relative assessments swisscantos portfolio managers look actively for investment opportunities on the market with which they achieve improvements in value for clients in the form of aboveaverage earnings adjusted for risks the investment philosophy is implemented systematically and consistently with the help of the latest quantitative analysis methods when arranging the asset management mandates for institutional clients swisscanto intensively takes account of individual needs and requirements the choice of the strategic asset allocation is dependent on the investment objectives and the ability to take risks thanks to its knowhow and experience the swisscanto specialists have clear ideas on the suitability of different benchmark variants and are in a position to give professional advice at every decision level swisscanto investment foundation elements for your investment success the swisscanto investment foundation today figures among the largest and best known investment foundations in switzerland its object is t